                  "content_html": "<p>{{letter_date}}</p><p>{{defendant_name}}<br>{{defendant_address}}<br>{{defendant_city_state_zip}}</p><p><strong>Re: Formal Demand for Payment - Property Damage ({{claim_amount}})</strong></p><p>Dear {{defendant_name}},</p><p>This letter is a formal demand for payment in the amount of <strong>${{claim_amount}}</strong> for property damage caused by your actions, based on the incident that occurred on {{incident_date}}.</p><p>Incident summary: {{claim_description}}</p><p>Please remit full payment within <strong>{{response_deadline}}</strong> from the date of this letter. If payment is not received, I will proceed with filing in <strong>{{court_name}}</strong>, <strong>{{county_name}}</strong>, without further notice.</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>{{claimant_name}}<br>{{claimant_address}}<br>{{claimant_city_state_zip}}</p>"
